		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Holding a weapon ready, you vanish into a myriad of illusory doubles that strike at your enemies. You teleport between your duplicates, attacking your chosen foes.</em></p><p><strong>Weapon Attack</strong></p><p>When you cast this spell, all of your targets must be within 30 ft. of each other.</p><ul><li><p>You conjure illusory duplicates of yourself that attack each target, then rapidly teleport to a convenient location near each target in sequence.</p></li><li><p>You make a single weapon attack against each target, ignoring range or cover.</p></li><li><p>You can then teleport to a location within 15 ft. of one of your targets or teleport back to your original position.</p></li></ul>",
